title: [Nielira Harbor, Acistira Pier]
description: Arched trellises of sable-washed wood ascend across the ebony-planked pier, the Nalfein ivy-entangled lattices engulfed in fragrant blooms of taerethil swept in hints of garnet.  A vine-framed haon sign hangs from the crossbeams, suspended from thin bronze chains alongside several spherical lanterns of merlot-colored glass.  Rectangular planters of blackened iron flank the edges of the pier, the stone and soil-filled containers covered in jewel-toned florals interspersed with vert foliage.
